{% block subject %}
    {% spaceless %}
        IMPORTANT: Specialty School Application Status for Confirmation Number: {{ submission }}
    {% endspaceless %}
{% endblock subject %}

{% block body_text %}
Hi {{ submission.parentEmail }},

Guardian of {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }}

RE: Specialty School Application Status for Confirmation Number: {{ submission }}

Congratulations! Your student is moving forward in consideration for a Specialty School Program(s).

{% if firstChoice is defined and firstChoice is not empty %}
    For your first choice: {{ firstChoice }}
    {% if firstChoiceMessage %}
        {{ firstChoiceMessage.specialRequirement }}
    {% else %}
        No further action is required of you at this time.  It is our goal to provide final notification regarding a student’s acceptance or non-acceptance into this program by March 17, 2015.
    {% endif %}
{% endif %}

{% if secondChoice is defined and secondChoice is not empty %}
    For your second choice: {{ secondChoice }}
    {% if secondChoiceMessage %}
       {{ secondChoiceMessage.specialRequirement }}
    {% else %}
        No further action is required.
    {% endif %}
{% endif %}

{% if thirdChoice is defined and thirdChoice is not empty %}
    For your third choice: {{ thirdChoice }}
    {% if thirdChoiceMessage %}
        {{ thirdChoiceMessage.specialRequirement }}
    {% else %}
        No further action is required of you at this time.  It is our goal to provide final notification regarding a student’s acceptance or non-acceptance into this program by March 17, 2015.
    {% endif %}
{% endif %}

Please save this email and/or record this confirmation number for your records.

Please add specialty@tusc.k12.al.us to your address list to ensure you receive future status updates of your application.

This is an automated email message from a mailbox that does not accept replies.  {{ 'magnet.contact'|trans|raw }}

Thanks,
Specialty School Program
{% endblock body_text %}

